OL,3,COscars now requires award voters to
OL,4,Cwatch all nominated movies
OL,6,FOscar voters will no longer be able to
OL,7,Fskip watching some nominated films, a
OL,8,Fmove that has left many on social
OL,9,Fmedia asking why it took so long.
OL,11,FThe Academy of Motion Picture Arts and
OL,12,FSciences announced on Monday that
OL,13,Fmembers must now watch all nominated
OL,14,Ffilms in each respective category to
OL,15,Fbe eligible to vote in the final round
OL,16,Fof Oscar voting.
OL,18,FUntil now, voters were only encouraged
OL,19,Fto watch the nominees and vote in
OL,20,Fcategories they felt qualified to
OL,21,Fjudge.
