OL,6,FIn recent years, the films actually
OL,7,Fwatched by Oscar voters have been seen
OL,8,Fas a key factor in determining the
OL,9,Fwinners.
OL,11,FAt the same time, the publication of
OL,12,Fanonymous Oscar ballots has often
OL,13,Ffeatured members confessing that they
OL,14,Fdidn't get around to watching some
OL,15,Fnotable films or not finishing
OL,16,Flengthier nominees.
OL,18,FThe Academy's new rule has sparked
OL,19,Fdebate online, with some questioning
OL,20,Fthe credibility of the awards.
