OL,6,F"So they voted against movies they
OL,7,Fdidn't even watch? I know why nobody
OL,8,Ftakes the Oscars seriously," one
OL,9,Fperson wrote on X.
OL,11,FAnother said: "It took almost 100
OL,12,Fyears for the Oscars to make sure the
OL,13,Fvoters actually watched the movies
OL,14,Fthey're voting for."
OL,16,FOne user said: "Big 'huh' moment...
OL,17,FIt's no wonder some of these seemed
OL,18,Flike they were awarded to movies that
OL,19,Fdidn't make sense."
