OL,6,F"This explains why movies like The
OL,7,FColour Purple, What's Love Got to Do
OL,8,FWith It, and Malcolm X were snubbed.
OL,9,FThese voters were NOT watching black
OL,10,Ffilms," they said.
OL,12,FThe Academy also introduced new rules
OL,13,Fon artificial intelligence (AI),
OL,14,Frefugee filmmakers, and its newly
OL,15,Flaunched casting category.
OL,17,FOn AI, it ruled that the use of
OL,18,Fgenerative tools would "neither help
OL,19,Fnor harm" a film's chances of being
OL,20,Fnominated.
